{"tid":1539721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原地踏步送中未撤！","createTime":"2019-09-04T10:17:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:17:39.000Z","uid":240086,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"78b7bd080ea72a0291c4a50c74c3e45acc98c373","tid":1539721,"uid":240086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:17:39.000Z","msg":"林鄭：保安局局長會喺復會後根據議事規則動議撤回修例<br />\n<br />\n根據議事規則64條，要喺<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">二讀辯論</span></span>上宣佈撤回，先算係正式撤回<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b6vwnzL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb6vwnzL.png&h=2af30cfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俾佢恢復二讀分分鐘通過二讀，直接過埋三讀<br />\n<br />\n唔係「撤又點」，係「<span style=\"color: red;\">根本未撤</span>」仲企圖恢復二讀<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}